Reasoning: 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with regular languages and rewriting systems. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also likely as the paper discusses the complexity of the representations. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is relevant as the paper deals with monoids and groups. 
- cs.GT (Group Theory) is relevant as the paper discusses abelian groups and group languages. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with the representation of languages using finitely many equivalence classes.
